<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.7.1">
<l>toṭarcaṅki likaicalārpi lāreṉṉat tūṅkupoṉ maṇiyolippap</l>
<l>paṭumumatap puṉaṟcōra vāraṇam paiyaniṉṟu vūrvatupō</l>
<l>luṭaṉkūṭik kiṇkiṇiyā ravārippa vuṭaimaṇi paṟaikaṟaṅka</l>
<l>taṭantāḷi ṇaikoṇṭucā raṅkapāṇi taḷarnaṭai naṭavāṉō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Like an elephant that stands slowly and ambles along</l>
<l>while the stream of ichor that appears in three places oozes out,</l>
<l>so that the hanging gold bells ring,</l>
<l>[and] the chain of shackles [on his] trunk clink and rattle,</l>
<l>will he [whose] hand [holds] the śārṅga bow</l>
<l>not come with a tottering walk with [his] pair of broad feet</l>
<l>so that the drum [like] bells on [his] waist cloth ring</l>
<l>[and his] tinkling anklets join in, jingling loudly?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
